HEADWORD: Discommode
<hw>Dis`com*mode"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Discommoded</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
